children.text: With Savings Catcher, if a competitor advertises a special deal for a lower price, we'll give you the difference.
Use your phone to scan the code from a Walmart receipt that's less than 7 days old.
Savings Catcher scans circulars from top competitors in your area for advertised deals that match the eligible items on your receipt.
If a lower advertised price is found, you get the difference on a Walmart eGift Card or Bluebird Card.
